{"tid":236371,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我從來都唔會因為自己廢而賴學校教得唔好","createTime":"2017-05-09T16:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T16:37:50.000Z","uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aead7e1fcf1bab5f08fa3c9f243a9a63c1ea3b5","tid":236371,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"有人話我因爲自己成績差所以賴學校<br />\n講真啦<br />\n要學野跟本上網咩資源都有尤其英文呢科<br />\n再唔得既話補習又好買書又好<br />\n全世界唔係得學校個件教到你野<br />\n我已經唔計呢堆人<br />\n-靠人事靠昔日母校關係拎教席既教畜<br />\n-缺乏危機感不思進取既長期合約hea教教畜<br />\n-讀書唔成讀水泡科冇mphil但係扮大牌既教畜<br />\n自學學到既野跟本就仲全面而且深入過學校學到既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過呢<br />\n我上面講既野都唔適用於基道中學<br />\n因為基道中學真係師資優良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdedeba79f5e02d9b41b318e6d5a619343fdcf0","tid":236371,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"利申讀緊FD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d08b85cd96b840533af45415a1e54cb9b0df0","tid":236371,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"回一句： 絕大部分教畜/教師都冇Mphil"}]}